what you found.

780
00:48:39,028 --> 00:48:40,780
If he saw it, why did he leave it out?

781
00:48:41,405 --> 00:48:43,491
Unless he was ordered
to frame my professor

782
00:48:43,574 --> 00:48:45,868
for drugging the victim to death.

783
00:48:50,039 --> 00:48:51,749
That's enough. He'd never do that.

784
00:49:03,594 --> 00:49:05,596
CITIZENS' POLICE
