of death would be a problem.

798
00:49:40,089 --> 00:49:41,799
But you were wrong.

799
00:49:42,383 --> 00:49:44,635
Both you and Han Joon-hwi
have been indicted.

800
00:49:45,761 --> 00:49:47,555
As joint principal offenders.

801
00:49:47,638 --> 00:49:48,514
JOINT OFFENDERS

802
00:49:48,597 --> 00:49:50,349
That is one groundless conclusion.

803
00:49:50,432 --> 00:49:51,892
It's not groundless.

804
00:49:51,976 --> 00:49:55,271
Han Joon-hwi used such a sneaky trick
to get you out.

805
00:49:55,354 --> 00:49:57,565
If you weren't in on it together,
why would he…

806
00:49:58,774 --> 00:49:59,733
go to such lengths?

807
00:49:59,817 --> 00:50:01,777
Oh, right.

808
00:50:03,112 --> 00:50:04,864
