809
00:50:09,201 --> 00:50:12,079
Everyone at the school seems shocked.

810
00:50:13,914 --> 00:50:16,667
Get a lawyer who used to be
a judge or prosecutor this time.

811
00:50:24,216 --> 00:50:27,386
