some shocking news earlier today.

812
00:50:28,470 --> 00:50:31,307
Professor Yang and Han Joon-hwi
have been indicted

813
00:50:31,390 --> 00:50:33,767
as joint principal offenders
in the murder.

814
00:50:34,602 --> 00:50:35,519
