816
00:50:37,855 --> 00:50:39,857
I'm sure you're all shocked by the news.

817
00:50:39,940 --> 00:50:41,275
Ms. Oh.

818
00:50:43,194 --> 00:50:44,778
I rushed to call this meeting

819
