830
00:51:13,265 --> 00:51:14,391
Will that be enough?

831
00:51:15,851 --> 00:51:17,519
Shouldn't he be fired?

832
00:51:17,603 --> 00:51:19,396
Isn't it almost the same thing?

833
00:51:20,522 --> 00:51:22,233
Telling him that he can't teach.

834
00:51:22,316 --> 00:51:23,567
No, it's different.

835
00:51:24,068 --> 00:51:25,694
He can keep his professor title.

836
00:51:27,655 --> 00:51:30,032
He can't teach the Criminal Code course
anymore.

837
00:51:30,115 --> 00:51:33,410
Professor Jung,
please continue to fill in.

838
00:51:33,494 --> 00:51:36,997
As for Joon-hwi,
I'll have the vice dean take over.

839
