866
00:54:10,609 --> 00:54:13,195
Are you going to flee
now that you've been indicted?

867
00:54:14,488 --> 00:54:15,364
You scumbag.

868
00:54:16,532 --> 00:54:19,076
I can't believe you schemed
with Yang Jong-hoon.

869
00:54:19,910 --> 00:54:20,828
"Schemed"?

870
00:54:25,749 --> 00:54:26,917
What's going on?

871
00:54:27,000 --> 00:54:28,377
What are you doing here?

872
00:54:30,504 --> 00:54:31,672
Why did you cremate him?

873
00:54:34,216 --> 00:54:38,220
They dug him up
for the second autopsy,

874
00:54:38,303 --> 00:54:39,638
so burying him again was--

875
00:54:39,721 --> 00:54:41,390
You observed the second autopsy.

876
00:54:42,891 --> 00:54:43,725
Yes, I did.

877
00:54:43,809 --> 00:54:46,728
Were there really signs of bleeding
in his brain?

878
00:54:49,314 --> 00:54:52,025
I couldn't actually observe it
because it was too gruesome.

879
00:54:52,109 --> 00:54:53,694
I fainted, so I saw nothing.

880
00:54:55,362 --> 00:54:56,488
Go help her.

881
00:55:03,495 --> 00:55:04,997
Because it was too gruesome?

882
00:55:05,080 --> 00:55:06,498
Was it not just an act?

883
00:55:07,082 --> 00:55:08,542
What are you talking about?

884
00:55:09,918 --> 00:55:11,211
What are you implying?

885
00:55:17,843 --> 00:55:21,263
Didn't you put on an act to give them time
to manipulate the results?

886
00:55:28,854 --> 00:55:30,981
Come on. Hurry.

887
00:55:31,064 --> 00:55:33,192
What are you suspicious of?

888
00:55:33,275 --> 00:55:35,486
-You said you know the director well.
-I sure do!

889
00:55:35,569 --> 00:55:37,070
-My gosh.
-Long time no see.

890
00:55:37,154 --> 00:55:40,574
