brain hemorrhage from a fall.

901
00:56:29,373 --> 00:56:31,166
I never told you to whip up two causes!

902
00:56:31,250 --> 00:56:32,501
I said it's not true!

903
00:56:36,713 --> 00:56:37,965
What's with that glare?

904
00:56:38,048 --> 00:56:39,800
I didn't do it.

905
00:56:41,051 --> 00:56:41,969
It wasn't me!

906
00:56:47,558 --> 00:56:48,600
Okay, thank you.

907
00:56:49,434 --> 00:56:51,812
The NFS asked them
to launch an investigation,

908
00:56:51,895 --> 00:56:53,981
so the examiner and the wife
have been booked.

909
00:56:54,606 --> 00:56:56,775
Oh, no. Joon-hwi must be shocked.

910
00:56:56,859 --> 00:56:59,736
It proves that he's innocent,
so he should call it even.

911
00:56:59,820 --> 00:57:02,114
I'm impressed that you pulled this off.

912
00:57:02,614 --> 00:57:04,116
All the digging has paid off.

913
00:57:04,616 --> 00:57:07,202
Joon-hwi managed to clear his name,
but Prof. Yang…

914
00:57:08,328 --> 00:57:10,163
Indictment isn't a joke.

915
00:57:10,247 --> 00:57:12,749
Take responsibility for indicting us
as joint offenders.

916
00:57:14,459 --> 00:57:16,211
You practically wrote a novel.

917
00:57:16,295 --> 00:57:18,589
You should attend my lecture
on joint offenders.

918
00:57:24,428 --> 00:57:25,888
Your charges will be dropped.

919
00:57:32,769 --> 00:57:33,937
I've been dismissed.

920
00:57:39,651 --> 00:57:41,194
WITHDRAWAL FORM

921
