927
00:58:15,562 --> 00:58:16,605
Still, I think--

928
00:58:16,688 --> 00:58:19,149
If there's no evidence,
it's just an assumption,

929
00:58:19,232 --> 00:58:20,317
which is unlike you.

930
00:58:20,400 --> 00:58:21,818
The sugar packet--

931
00:58:21,902 --> 00:58:23,779
I'm glad they know you didn't take it.

932
00:58:28,867 --> 00:58:29,868
I'm glad…

933
00:58:35,290 --> 00:58:36,166
